   <h2>
    NetID Authentication
   </h2>
   The Experiment Recruiter uses the UA NetID WebAuth service for authentication.
   <br/>
   <br/>
   By clicking on the
   <b>
    Login / Register
   </b>
   button, you will be taken to the the University of Arizona's  WebAuth Login Page.  Once you successfully login with your UA NetID, you will be returned here.
